{"tid":1151611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 打算貼「反修例」街貼","createTime":"2019-05-12T15:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T18:15:45.000Z","uid":113373,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"308dffea0a6604dd0d8e766e75cbe4fa97ce59a8","tid":1151611,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"內容同我之前洗版嘅差唔多<br />\n大家覺得有咩內容要改<br />\n歡迎留低意見<br />\n一星期內會印同貼<br />\n亦好歡迎大家幫手印同喺自己嘅地區貼<br />\n我就會喺屯元天一帶貼<br />\n<br />\n=================================<br />\n<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港人直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港送你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)"},{"pid":"4cf0a1c126fc23169ae2497a9191b398fbacb5b1","tid":1151611,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2fe8bc9e48d4f2e3e88f7507e849c1d386f884","tid":1151611,"uid":39181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"af302da8567aca4f63018a54e65cade60f818452","tid":1151611,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"更正標題<br />\n係 街招<br />\n<br />\n打錯"},{"pid":"3a34bbf96aebcb531954b3510134eefba09ec127","tid":1151611,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"有冇考慮同泛民區議員傾下一齊合作？"},{"pid":"1b85a062d99151687fe2faaa7a01e139c5a56171","tid":1151611,"uid":113373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a34bbf96aebcb531954b3510134eefba09ec127","tid":1151611,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,